                     <note>- The explicit of Text I has been left incomplete: some words are missing
                        (cp. Ms.<ref type="mss" corresp="ESap056">AP-056</ref>, <locus target="#44va">44va</locus>).</note>
                     <note>- Text II contains 11 miracles, which are not numbered; they are the same
                        and in the same sequence as in Ms.<ref type="mss" corresp="ESap046">AP-046</ref>.</note>
                     <note>- <locus target="#54rb">54rb</locus> l.10-54vb: final supplication
                        formula at the end of Text II.</note>
                  </msItem>
